<div type="edition" xml:lang="und" rendition="class:nāgarī maturity:undetermined">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>vīraśrī gajapti gauḍesvara paratāpa pṛsottamadeva māhārājaṅkara vije rāije samasta 17 sarāi
<lb n="2"/>dhanū kri 10 vuthavāre kaliṅgadaṇḍapāṭhaparicchā valakhīdāsa māhāpātraṅkara Athikāre jīuradesa deu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>la bhogaparīkṣā vithanasara māhāti Adhiṣṭāṇe pañcāni pāñcaparakraṇa vehora pe
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ko niddhāramāṇī kīrajātadesa bhurapalligrāmakū pāla(ka)rajāṅkara Āigā <g type="danda">.</g> pramāṇe
<lb n="5"/>Amṛtamaṇāyi deuḷasīmaṅkū jītī karadīyā <g type="danda">.</g> dacchiṇakosavisāra jajapalligrāma Egrāmajā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>vata candrāṇe bhoga karīva <g type="danda">.</g> E grāmara bhūiru <g type="danda">.</g> Ācārījadasai dāsīki bhūidūi
<lb n="7"/>maṭhabhoga Akūa <g type="danda">.</g> Eka śaiva E pāara Āura jete bhūi savū māṇīki kośikāre Āe karive [<g type="danda">.</g>]
<lb n="8"/>Ethakū bhogaparīkṣā rājaparakaraṇa pakādhi pākaparakaraṇaṅkara sanamata <g type="danda">.</g> <gap reason="lost" quantity="7" unit="character"/> nare<supplied reason="omitted">si</supplied>ṅga
<lb n="9" break="no"/>nā(nā)thāreva madhmau [<g type="danda">.</g>] śrī śrī śrī śrī śrī [<g type="ddanda">.</g>]<note n="351-1">The continuation of this inscription is covered by a modern wall.</note>
</p>

